    <item>
      <title>Institutional assets on-chain at J.P. Morgan.</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/case-studies/jpm-onyx/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/case-studies/jpm-onyx/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I was super excited to see J.P. Morgan and Blackrock&amp;rsquo;s public announcement about their on-chain collateral management pilot.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I worked on the interface for the initial pilot of this product during my time with J.P. Morgan Onyx—the company&amp;rsquo;s blockchain-focused division. This particular project solved a major (and expensive) painpoint for complex trading organizations: collateral management.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;style&gt;&#xA; &#xA;&#xA;.testimonial-block {&#xA; &#xA;  box-sizing: border-box;&#xA;  width: 100%;&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;.testimonial-block__card {&#xA; &#xA;  display: flex;&#xA;  flex-direction: row;&#xA;  align-items: flex-start;&#xA;  gap: 1.5rem;&#xA;  box-sizing: border-box;&#xA;  margin: 2rem;&#xA;  padding: 1rem;&#xA;  background-color: var(--bg-inverse-primary);&#xA;  box-shadow: var(--shadow-callout-block);&#xA;  border-radius: 1px;&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;.testimonial-block :is(.p-sm, .p-sm-heavy) {&#xA;  padding-top: 0;&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;.testimonial-block__photo-wrap {&#xA;  flex-shrink: 0;&#xA;  width: 4.5rem;&#xA;  height: 11.5rem;&#xA;  overflow: hidden;&#xA;  box-shadow: var(--shadow-callout-block);&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;.testimonial-block__photo {&#xA;  display: block;&#xA;  width: 100%;&#xA;  height: 100%;&#xA;  object-fit: cover;&#xA;  object-position: center top;&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;.testimonial-block__content {&#xA;  flex: 1;&#xA;  min-width: 0;&#xA;  display: flex;&#xA;  flex-direction: column;&#xA;  gap: 1.5rem;&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;.testimonial-block__quotes {&#xA;  margin: 0;&#xA;  display: flex;&#xA;  flex-direction: column;&#xA;  gap: 0.375rem;&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;.testimonial-block__big-quote,&#xA;.testimonial-block__small-quote,&#xA;.testimonial-block__name,&#xA;.testimonial-block__title,&#xA;.testimonial-block__company {&#xA;  margin: 0;&#xA;  color: var(--text-inverse-primary);&#xA;  text-align: left;&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;.serif .testimonial-block__big-quote,&#xA;.testimonial-block__big-quote {&#xA;  font-size: 2rem;&#xA;  font-family: var(--font-family-serif-display);&#xA;  font-weight: var(--font-weight-heavy);&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;.testimonial-block__small-quote {&#xA;  font-style: italic;&#xA;  color: var(--text-inverse-secondary);&#xA;  font-family: var(--font-family-serif-text);&#xA;  font-size: 1rem;&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;.testimonial-block__name {&#xA;  display: flex;&#xA;  flex-wrap: wrap;&#xA;  gap: 0.125rem;&#xA;  font-family: var(--font-family-serif-text);&#xA;  font-size: var(--font-size-p);&#xA;  font-weight: var(--font-weight-heavy);&#xA;  line-height: var(--line-height-heading);&#xA;  color: var(--text-inverse-primary);&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;.testimonial-block__first-name,&#xA;.testimonial-block__last-name {&#xA;  color: inherit;&#xA;  font: inherit;&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;.testimonial-block__title,&#xA;.testimonial-block__company {&#xA;  color: var(--text-inverse-secondary);&#xA;  font-family: var(--font-family-serif-text);&#xA;  font-size: var(--font-size-sm);&#xA;  line-height: var(--line-height-body);&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;.testimonial-block__attribution {&#xA;  display: flex;&#xA;  flex-direction: column;&#xA;  gap: 0.125rem;&#xA;  margin: 0;&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;@media screen and (max-width: 30em) {&#xA;  .testimonial-block__card {&#xA;    flex-direction: column;&#xA;  }&#xA;&#xA;  .testimonial-block__photo-wrap {&#xA;    width: 100%;&#xA;    height: 8rem;&#xA;  }&#xA;}&#xA;&lt;/style&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;  &#xA;&#xA;  &#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;        &#xA;      &#xA;        &#xA;      &#xA;        &#xA;          &#xA;            &#xA;          &#xA;          &#xA;            &#xA;          &#xA;        &#xA;      &#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;      &#xA;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;testimonial-block&#34; role=&#34;group&#34; aria-label=&#34;Testimonial from Lawrence Lipkin&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;div class=&#34;testimonial-block__card&#34;&gt;&#xA;          &lt;div class=&#34;testimonial-block__photo-wrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;img class=&#34;testimonial-block__photo&#34;&#xA;                 src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/testimonial-avatars/Lawrence-Lipkin.jpeg&#34;&#xA;                 alt=&#34;Lawrence Lipkin&#34;&#xA;                 loading=&#34;lazy&#34; /&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;          &lt;div class=&#34;testimonial-block__content&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;div class=&#34;testimonial-block__quotes&#34;&gt;&#xA;              &lt;p class=&#34;testimonial-block__big-quote serif-display&#34;&gt;able to learn complex domains quickly, and uses his superb story-telling skills to re-shape and re-frame business ideas into cohesive narratives that enable cross-functional teams to collaborate more effectively.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
